The British High Commission has no authority to intervene on behalf of British nationals of Bangladeshi origin with regard to land or property problems. The High Commission can provide a list of local lawyers.
There is an Expatriate Help Cell of Bangladesh Police, the cell offers services to expatriates including dual nationals/British Bangladeshis. Expatriate Help Cell contact details:
Mobile: +88 01769690019
Email: expatriatehelp@police.gov.bd
Bangladesh Police website: www.police.gov.bd
